<list_item><loc_86><loc_332><loc_443><loc_369>Monetar5r compensation shall be granted  only when the overtime  service is rendered  for at least two (2) hours. For services  rendered  less than two (2) hours, the default compensation shall be provided  through Vacation Service Credits (VSC) subject to existing DepEd  and Civil Service Commission (CSC) guidelines. 6</list_item>
<list_item><loc_86><loc_378><loc_443><loc_408>Teachers reassigned to perform non-teaching functions including those who are designated as Teacher-in-Charge  (TIC)  with teaching  load shall not be covered by this poliry but by CSC-DBM JC No. O2 and DO No. 30, s. 2O 16 and any subsequent  related  issuances. 7</list_item>
